data.description: 706 Shamrock rd , Bel Air MD is a stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath Split Foyer home in the heart of  Bel Air, MD!   Step inside to discover a home that is well maintained and move in ready.Recent uppgrades include a brand-new HVAC system installed in 2020, a new roof in 2016, and updated windows and a brand new fence.  The main leve features refinished hardwood floors throughout and freshly painted walls, creating an inviting ambiance. The living room flows into the dining room, providing a perfect setting for both everyday living and entertaining. Open the door to a world of possibilities with direct access to the rear deck and a sprawling backyard.  The kitchen  has been recently modernized with beautiful cabinets and numerous upgrades. Upstairs, the primary bedroom boasts a fully renovated en-suite bathroom, complemented by two additional generously sized bedrooms and a full bathroom in the hallway.  The lower level is made for comfort and relaxation, featuring a spacious open room with a cozy fireplace, a convenient half bathroom, and direct access to the backyard and attached garage. The fourth bedroom, could double as an office, adds flexibility to the floor plan.  Practicality meets style in the utility room, offering ample space for laundry and utilities. The wide-open backyard is an entertainer's paradise, seamlessly connecting to both the main and lower levels.  Don't miss your chance to call this Bel Air beauty home. Schedule a showing today.
